      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ServiceDefaults - Call it was you want, Core? Shared? Whatever\n    - common configuration to applied to all services that are part of this app.\n    - includes (ours) OTEL, SRE (retries, circuit breakers, etc.)\n    - could (should?) also have the security stuff here.",
