      "text": "Dev Environment Support Stuff\n(tools never meant for production, but\nmake the developer experience better.\n(like viewing openapi specs, tools\nto see databases, etc.)\n\nOTEL Collector and Visualizer\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
